headline: Alcon's Tryptyr Adds Growth, But Valuation Keeps Shares On 'Hold'
summary: Alcon posts steady growth in Vision Care and Surgical, with new drug and therapy launches ahead but execution risks persist. Read why ALC stock is a hold.

headline: 1 S&P 500 Stock with Competitive Advantages and 2 to Steer Clear Of
summary: While the S&P 500 (^GSPC) includes industry leaders, not every stock in the index is a winner. Some companies are past their prime, weighed down by poor execution, weak financials, or structural headwinds.
